Package: epuR
Type: Package
Title: Collect and Process Economic Policy Uncertainty Data
Version: 0.1.1
Author: Lingbing Feng
Maintainer: Lingbing Feng <fenglb88@gmail.com>
Description: Provides functions to collect the economic policy uncertainty
  (EPU) and related index data from the official  website
  <https://www.policyuncertainty.com/index.html> in real time.
  Deals with date format issuse and returns an xts object to
  facilitate further time series data manipulation and
  analysis.
License: GPL
URL: https://github.com/Lingbing/epuR
BugReports: https://github.com/Lingbing/epuR/issues
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Imports: openxlsx, xts, zoo, stats, stringr, lubridate, data.table
RoxygenNote: 7.1.0
VignetteBuilder: knitr
Suggests: knitr, rmarkdown, dygraphs
